203
00:12:45,279 --> 00:12:48,959
The best way to solve all of those is to just do it.

204
00:12:48,959 --> 00:12:51,519
If you don't know what to build, just build something.

205
00:12:51,519 --> 00:12:54,079
If you don't know what to tweet about, just tweet anything.

206
00:12:54,079 --> 00:12:55,440
