208
00:12:58,399 --> 00:13:00,240
So, you either tweet something and you'll get no likes.

209
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:01,200
You're like, "Okay, that doesn't work.

210
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,560
I can move on to the next thing."

211
00:13:02,560 --> 00:13:04,240
Or you'll build something and it won't work.

212
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,000
